selected_rate.name: E-ELEC Residential Time of Use (Electric Home)
selected_rate.description:
This optional schedule applies to individually-metered electric service to residential
customers who have one or more of the following qualifying electric technologies:
• Electric vehicle charging;
• Energy storage; or
• Electric heat pump for water heating or climate control (space heating and/or
cooling).
